# Plan: Add `image-text-to-text` Pipeline to Transformers.js

## Context

The Transformers.js library already has `AutoModelForImageTextToText` (src/models.js:8736) supporting 11 VLM architectures (LLaVA, Qwen2-VL, Idefics3, Florence2, PaliGemma, etc.), but there is no corresponding pipeline task to provide a high-level API. The existing `image-to-text` pipeline only takes images (no text prompt). This change adds an `image-text-to-text` pipeline that accepts both an image and a text prompt, enabling use cases like visual question answering and image-grounded text generation.

## Files to Modify

